  "description": {
   "en": "One day, a transfer student named Atami suddenly appeared in the countryside. Everyone is intrigued by the rare existence of a transfer student. He hurt his leg as a result of an accident and is still suffering from the after effects. He is sincere to everyone, and those around him have always cared for him. On the other hand, Kamonomiya, who is part of the track and field club, is a straightforward and obedient person who is unable to tell lies. For some reasson, he is the only person who can see the true feelings of Atami, who thinks the current situation is '' depressing.'' It has something to do with their past together... A boy who wants to run and a boy who can no longer run meet and are growing into adults. A story of friendship that sweeps through youth."
